     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"The LIPS and Major Schemes evaluation programmes captures any pedestrian, cycle, bus and freight outcomes as a result of improvement schemes.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "The evaluation programme looks at a variety of scheme types using common and consistent evaluation methodologies.",
     "The outcome  reports provide boroughs and planners with a valuable resource when planning schemes and street interventions, highlighting both successful schemes and those that did not realise all planned objectives. This helps improve design and provide better value for money.",
     "We have published a best practice guide to help monitor pedestrian outcomes more easily and reliably.",
     "{\"template\":\"listgroup\",\"style\":\"nocard\",\"links\":[{\"title\":\"Measuring pedestrian activity\",\"url\":\"/cdn/static/cms/documents/measuring-pedestrian-activity.pdf\",\"icon\":\"download\",\"size\":\"PDF 1.28MB\",\"image\":{}}],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
